Package eu.wauz.wauzcore.players.classes

This package contains the choosable character classes and subclasses.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WauzPlayerClass
    A class, that can be chosen by a player.
    WauzPlayerSubclass
    A subclass / mastery, that belongs to a player class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseClass
    A template for a class, that can be chosen by a player.
    BaseSubclass
    A template for a subclass / mastery, that belongs to a player class.
    ClassCleric
    A class, that can be chosen by a player.
    ClassMage
    A class, that can be chosen by a player.
    ClassRogue
    A class, that can be chosen by a player.
    ClassWarrior
    A class, that can be chosen by a player.
    Learnable
    A skill or similar, that can be learned through a subclass / mastery.
    WauzPlayerClassPool
    This class is used to register, find and select classes.
    WauzPlayerClassStats
    The starting stats and passive skills of a class.
